text: Vera Hohlfeld (born 24 February 1972) is a road cyclist from Germany. She represented her nation at the 1996 Summer Olympics where she finished fourth in the women's road race. ==References== ==External links== * profile at sports-reference.com Category:German female cyclists Category:Cyclists at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic cyclists of Germany Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Erfurt Category:1972 births
